: 374, \"to\": 382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were all so proud that in 2024, we were given the platform tobe,\\\" says Doll, known for her appearance on the reality showRuPaul's Drag Raceand as the host ofDrag Race France.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995790213145087, \"rank\": 0.00039740145803429, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the platform tobe\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"Doll\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"her appearance\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"showRuPaul's Drag Raceand\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the host\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't until the next day that Doll realized she was also at the center of an Olympic-sized backlash.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next day\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"Doll\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-sized backlash\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Catholic bishopsdecriedthe ceremony's \\\"derision and mockery of Christianity.\\\"\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.971701853231432, \"rank\": 0.02072628742805199, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.99984077246578, \"rank\": 0.00015911266287