gram\": \"Personal attacks\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"her DMs\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then came the threats: \\\"we know where you live,\\\" \\\"we have guns,\\\" \\\"we will cut your throat.\\\"\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the threats\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"guns\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"your throat\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other performers were getting harassed, too.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other performers\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A special police unit dedicated to fighting hate crimes was tasked with investigating online abuse targeted at lesbian activist DJ Barbara Butch, the Paris prosecutor's officetold the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0242554944064701e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999980432221, \"rank\": 1.9567270887428776e-09, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A special police unit\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"hate crimes\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As queer people, we are used to being criticized on social media,\\\" says Doll, who is from Marseille but now lives in New York.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1716, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999997165150891, \"rank\": 2.8348023348373553e-07, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999915216904, \"rank\": 8.478392005280715e-09, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"Doll\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when we saw they were using religion \\u2026 in order to attack us, this felt like a low blow that we did not see coming.\\\"\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"a low blow\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Behind the messages were the usual crowd of anonymous trolls, hiding behind accounts with no names or profile pictures.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the messages\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the usual crowd\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymous trolls\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"a