 {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"the catwalk scene\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"the cast\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"little pedos\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The post remains visible on the platform with a fact-check label that says: \\\"There is no evidence that any of the people in the photograph are pedophiles.\\\"\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The post\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"a fact-check label\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"no evidence\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"the photograph\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"pedophiles\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response, Doll, who features in the video next to Butch, decided to sue Fox for defamation in France.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9343253486708852, \"rank\": 0.0702909858859897, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995790213145087, \"rank\": 0.00039740145803429, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"Doll\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"defamation\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to sue him personally, because I want him to understand that he cannot continue to use us for his personal agenda and his words matter,\\\" she says, \\\"The message that he sends to his fan base matters.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"his personal agenda\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"his words\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"The message\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"his fan base matters\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's an enabler for hate and homophobia and transphobia.\\\"\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2802, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"transphobia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an enabler\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"hate\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"homophobia\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Representatives for Fox and X did not reply to WIRED's requests for comment.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9343253486708852, \"rank\": 0.0702909858859897, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wired_UK\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9639384785646412e-33, \"text\": \"WIRED\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wired_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wired_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Representatives\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"comment\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Doll, the concern is that the type of rhetoric that came in response to the opening ceremony, if left to spread unchecked, could inspire offline violence.\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Doll\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"the concern\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"rhetoric\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"offline violence\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Queer people could be literally murdered in the streets,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Queer people\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very important that we stop allowing this kind of rhetoric to demonize queer people.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"rhetoric\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not demons.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"demons\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not trying to attack religion and families.\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rel